name: kml2geojson
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "kml2geojson" %}
{% set version = "5.1.0" %}


package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/kml2geojson-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 76a69f598e55d2eff90332e87ee9480c36120f60e6f5d6b5aaeba63ce92a3dfa

build:
  number: 0
  noarch: python
  entry_points:
    - k2g = kml2geojson.cli:k2g
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6,<4.0
    - poetry >=1,<2
  run:
    - click >=8.0.1,<9.0.0
    - python >=3.6,<4.0

test:
  imports:
    - kml2geojson
  commands:
    - pip check
    - k2g --help
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://pypi.org/project/kml2geojson/
  summary: A Python library to covert KML files to GeoJSON files
  license: MIT
  license_file: LICENSE.txt

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - ickc
